      <title>Flask&#43;HTML5实现服务器推送事件</title>
      <link>/posts/flask-html5%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%81%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6/</link>
